{"tid":401453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楊潤雄下週一至三訪京　蔡若蓮署任教育局長","createTime":"2017-09-15T15:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T01:44:23.000Z","uid":51904,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5131d78aec8a2e9be5080c25e600a4196e608bec","tid":401453,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:17:58.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄將於下星期一（9月18日）傍晚啟程前往北京訪問，周三（9月20日）回港。期間由副局長蔡若蓮署任教育局局長，顯示蔡若蓮經歷喪子之痛後現已回到工作崗位。<br />\n<br />\n政府新聞稿指，楊潤雄訪京期間將會與中國教育部官員舉行會議，及禮節性拜訪國務院港澳事務辦公室及北京市教育委員會。他亦會於北京出席活動，與一批正在內地升讀大學的香港學生會面，了解他們的日常生活情況及需要。"},{"pid":"9dd5d3cdeb9c1feb6701e69f8219e3b971774ec6","tid":401453,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:28:32.000Z","msg":"若蓮喪子，升官發財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2a1ba1fbf2813d2c6d12cc26dbcc4423ed0b16","tid":401453,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:32:11.000Z","msg":"咁都唔辭職仲繼續做 痴撚線女人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74cf4ca0a52122ddda7833fe470e113648ac7c64","tid":401453,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:38:42.000Z","msg":"升官發財死大仔"},{"pid":"753a6bbd4247c6e0b069d0eec40f00e67fa72c78","tid":401453,"uid":1082,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>升官發財死大仔</blockquote><br />\n死大仔先可以署任三日， 咁坐正咪要。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5db55a4eaae7c43acf212fdc9e35973509fcb75","tid":401453,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T17:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>升官發財死大仔</blockquote><br />\n死大仔先可以署任三日， 咁坐正咪要。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知點解大家覺得死一個仔就咁開心<br />\n呢種人為左共產黨利益, 死曬全家報國都唔覺得係咩一件事<br />\n共產黨最多換過另一條命頂上"},{"pid":"a3306a56b8a1deef0922b1403e7056bf916369dc","tid":401453,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:18:27.000Z","msg":"恭喜蔡副局坐正"},{"pid":"310c546bba669d83791f81d460c3652296d3abd9","tid":401453,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T18:39:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7773a35754979de6222016580ad86f31eb93ffe6","tid":401453,"uid":188201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5131d78aec8a2e9be5080c25e600a4196e608bec","tid":401453,"uid":51904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T15:17:58.000Z","msg":"教育局局長楊潤雄將於下星期一（9月18日）傍晚啟程前往北京訪問，周三（9月20日）回港。期間由副局長蔡若蓮署任教育局局長，顯示蔡若蓮經歷喪子之痛後現已回到工作崗位。<br />\n<br />\n政府新聞稿指，楊潤雄訪京期間將會與中國教育部官員舉行會議，及禮節性拜訪國務院港澳事務辦公室及北京市教育委員會。他亦會於北京出席活動，與一批正在內地升讀大學的香港學生會面，了解他們的日常生活情況及需要。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T01:44:23.000Z","msg":"教育局局長可唔可以做啲野<br />\n<br />\n一個老師同一時間教200人其實係唔係犯法？<br />\n元朗上 live 兩層樓幾間房坐200人每間班房有一個傀儡唔係教書嘅老師，而真正教書嘅應該只有一個老師，咁樣走法律罅嘅話一個人同時教200人我記得好似係犯法，我諗住去申訴專員公署問吓教育署有冇造漏野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片來自 billy ng Instagram <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/05/083254_bfa29f1d4a66cc2a9425b5d9d6af6e85.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F083254_bfa29f1d4a66cc2a9425b5d9d6af6e85.png&h=15e4c8cb&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}